    <item>
      <title>Global burden of brain disorders surpasses cardiovascular disease and cancer</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/global-burden-of-brain-disorders-surpasses-cardiovascular-disease-and-cancer/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 15 Jul 2023 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/global-burden-of-brain-disorders-surpasses-cardiovascular-disease-and-cancer/</guid>
      <description>&lt;nav id=&#34;TableOfContents&#34;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;ul&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#from-mdedgehttpswwwmdedgecomneurologyarticle264086neurologyglobal-burden-brain-disorders-surpasses-cardiovascular-diseaseecdwnl_eve_230715_mdedge&#34;&gt;From &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mdedge.com/neurology/article/264086/neurology/global-burden-brain-disorders-surpasses-cardiovascular-disease?ecd=WNL_EVE_230715_mdedge&#34;&gt;MDEdge&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#vitamin-d-inhaled-thru-the-nose-gets-some-directly-to-the-brain&#34;&gt;Vitamin D inhaled thru the nose gets some directly to the brain&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#vitamin-d-preventstreats-multiple-sclerosis-and-10-other-brain-disorders&#34;&gt;Vitamin D prevents/treats Multiple Sclerosis and 10 other brain disorders&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;          &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/li&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/nav&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;from-mdedgehttpswwwmdedgecomneurologyarticle264086neurologyglobal-burden-brain-disorders-surpasses-cardiovascular-diseaseecdwnl_eve_230715_mdedge&#34;&gt;From &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mdedge.com/neurology/article/264086/neurology/global-burden-brain-disorders-surpasses-cardiovascular-disease?ecd=WNL_EVE_230715_mdedge&#34;&gt;MDEdge&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Brain disorders, including mental illness, neurologic conditions, and stroke, account for more than 15% of all health loss worldwide – more than either cardiovascular disease or cancer – at huge cost to health care systems and society, an analysis of data from the most recent Global Burden of Disease (GBD) study shows.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
